For the next script version

This crash shows the script should eventually be patched to support:

--hf_offline

and internally load SentenceTransformer(..., local_files_only=True) or set the Hugging Face offline flags before importing/loading models. It should also checkpoint after NAICS and after qe4ar so a network hiccup cannot erase supervised-training progress.

But for right now, the practical fix is:

Run offline mode + restart with existing embedding caches.

You were very close to the finish. The machine tripped over a phone call to Hugging Face, not over the actual prediction machinery.
